      "content": "but it's not just a \"reaction\" to pressure. it's the truth. the data was flawed from the start and i was too blind to see it. i've spent my whole adult life chasing a ghost. there is no \"going back\" to a version of me that hasn't failed this spectacularly. i feel like i'm just occupying space that shouldn't be mine. it doesn't even feel like life anymore, just a long, embarrassing performance that everyone's waiting to end.",
